translate portuguese loveinterestmontage_f5af9ece:

    # wt "I built a device that could send messages between worlds."
    wt "Construí um dispositivo capaz de enviar mensagens entre mundos."

# game/Scenes/Update20/loveinterestmontage.rpy:220
translate portuguese loveinterestmontage_b6a5943b:

    # pc "Just while I was gone? That was quick."
    pc "Enquanto estive fora? Foi rápido."

# game/Scenes/Update20/loveinterestmontage.rpy:221
translate portuguese loveinterestmontage_c5e0562a:

    # wt "I was motivated."
    wt "Eu estava motivado."

# game/Scenes/Update20/loveinterestmontage.rpy:224
translate portuguese loveinterestmontage_ccb1fefb:

    # pc "So, I could talk to my dad? Or anyone else that I met there?"
    pc "Então, eu poderia falar com o meu pai? Ou com qualquer outra pessoa que eu tenha conhecido lá?"

# game/Scenes/Update20/loveinterestmontage.rpy:225
translate portuguese loveinterestmontage_85724e3f:

    # wt "Theoretically. They don't have any way to speak back though. Yet."
    wt "Teoricamente. Mas eles não têm como responder. Ainda."

# game/Scenes/Update20/loveinterestmontage.rpy:226
translate portuguese loveinterestmontage_b0652138:

    # wt "Is that something that you'd want to do?"
    wt "É algo que gostarias de fazer?"

# game/Scenes/Update20/loveinterestmontage.rpy:227
translate portuguese loveinterestmontage_5b22d737:

    # pc "Maybe."
    pc "Talvez."

# game/Scenes/Update20/loveinterestmontage.rpy:230
translate portuguese loveinterestmontage_b67e5d2c:

    # wt "I'm not sure why you lost so much time during the return trip."
    wt "Não sei bem por que perdeste tanto tempo durante a viagem de regresso."

# game/Scenes/Update20/loveinterestmontage.rpy:231
translate portuguese loveinterestmontage_4a7e2d03:

    # wt "It seems like time moves faster over there, so less time should have passed here."
    wt "Parece que o tempo passa mais depressa por lá, por isso deveria ter passado menos tempo aqui."

# game/Scenes/Update20/loveinterestmontage.rpy:232
translate portuguese loveinterestmontage_f52c90f3:

    # wt "But you had that beard when you came back and a month passed while you were gone."
    wt "Mas tu tinhas aquela barba quando voltaste e passou um mês enquanto estiveste fora."

# game/Scenes/Update20/loveinterestmontage.rpy:235
translate portuguese loveinterestmontage_522730c7:

    # wt "More studies will have to be done."
    wt "Será necessário fazer mais estudos."

# game/Scenes/Update20/loveinterestmontage.rpy:236
translate portuguese loveinterestmontage_7dc54a4b:

    # wt "Can I count on you to help me with them? I'd love to hire you, now that you're almost done with school."
    wt "Posso contar contigo para me ajudares com eles? Adoraria contratar-te, agora que estás quase a terminar a escola."

# game/Scenes/Update20/loveinterestmontage.rpy:237
translate portuguese loveinterestmontage_39c52a0e:

    # wt "I believe graduation is this weekend?"
    wt "Acho que a formatura é este fim de semana?"

# game/Scenes/Update20/loveinterestmontage.rpy:240
translate portuguese loveinterestmontage_38559d3f:

    # pc "Graduation!"
    pc "Formatura!"

# game/Scenes/Update20/loveinterestmontage.rpy:241
translate portuguese loveinterestmontage_ac2fc58a:

    # pc "Fuck..."
    pc "Foda-se..."

# game/Scenes/Update20/loveinterestmontage.rpy:245
translate portuguese loveinterestmontage_05caf076:

    # et "You missed some assignments and the final..."
    et "Faltaste a alguns trabalhos e ao exame final..."

# game/Scenes/Update20/loveinterestmontage.rpy:247
translate portuguese loveinterestmontage_b3be8a82:

    # et "... but don't worry, honey, I took care of it for you."
    et "... mas não te preocupes, querido, eu tratei disso por ti."

# game/Scenes/Update20/loveinterestmontage.rpy:248
translate portuguese loveinterestmontage_399bdc0f:

    # pc "Really?"
    pc "A sério?"

# game/Scenes/Update20/loveinterestmontage.rpy:251
translate portuguese loveinterestmontage_962b180d:

    # et "Of course. You're a smart boy. I know you would have done well on them."
    et "Claro. És um rapaz inteligente. Sei que te terias saído bem neles."

# game/Scenes/Update20/loveinterestmontage.rpy:252
translate portuguese loveinterestmontage_486294f6:

    # et "I'm not going to stop you from graduating because you had something more important going on in your life for a while."
    et "Não vou impedir-te de te formares só porque tiveste algo mais importante a acontecer na tua vida durante algum tempo."

# game/Scenes/Update20/loveinterestmontage.rpy:255
translate portuguese loveinterestmontage_08a658e1:

    # et "Besides... I take care of you and I know you'll take care of me later."
    et "Além disso... Eu cuido de ti e sei que mais tarde vais cuidar de mim."

# game/Scenes/Update20/loveinterestmontage.rpy:256
translate portuguese loveinterestmontage_e4d26afc:

    # et "Right?"
    et "Certo?"

# game/Scenes/Update20/loveinterestmontage.rpy:257
translate portuguese loveinterestmontage_78bd7358:

    # pc "Damn right."
    pc "Podes ter a certeza."

# game/Scenes/Update20/loveinterestmontage.rpy:259
translate portuguese loveinterestmontage_dd7b6f24:

    # et "... but if you sit and take the final real quick and you pass, you'll still be able to graduate."
    et "... mas se te sentares e fizeres a prova final rapidinho e passares, ainda vais conseguir formar-te."

# game/Scenes/Update20/loveinterestmontage.rpy:260
translate portuguese loveinterestmontage_e9e45599:

    # pc "Oh yes please, Mrs. McGee. That would be great."
    pc "Sim, por favor, Sra. McGee. Isso seria ótimo."

# game/Scenes/Update20/loveinterestmontage.rpy:266
translate portuguese loveinterestmontage_d0ae05fb:

    # et "This is very good. You'll pass."
    et "Isto está muito bom. Vais passar."

# game/Scenes/Update20/loveinterestmontage.rpy:267
translate portuguese loveinterestmontage_b6c4c749:

    # et "I knew you were a smart boy."
    et "Eu sabia que eras um rapaz inteligente."

# game/Scenes/Update20/loveinterestmontage.rpy:268
translate portuguese loveinterestmontage_6f49be4e:

    # pc "Thanks so much, Mrs. McGee."
    pc "Muito obrigado, Sra. McGee."

# game/Scenes/Update20/loveinterestmontage.rpy:272
translate portuguese loveinterestmontage_d08e2cf8:

    # sst "Yeah, you missed a few things..."
    sst "Sim, falhaste algumas coisas..."

# game/Scenes/Update20/loveinterestmontage.rpy:274
translate portuguese loveinterestmontage_322a44f2:

    # sst "...but I'm not going to fail you."
    sst "... mas não te vou reprovar."

# game/Scenes/Update20/loveinterestmontage.rpy:277
translate portuguese loveinterestmontage_97e19796:

    # sst "I need you to graduate so that I feel less guilty about fucking you every chance I get."
    sst "Preciso que te formes para me sentir menos culpada por te foder sempre que posso."

# game/Scenes/Update20/loveinterestmontage.rpy:278
translate portuguese loveinterestmontage_dc418b49:

    # pc "Really? So I'm good?"
    pc "A sério? Então estou bem?"

# game/Scenes/Update20/loveinterestmontage.rpy:281
translate portuguese loveinterestmontage_8e879040:

    # sst "You might have to do some private studies... but yeah, you're so good, baby."
    sst "Talvez tenhas de fazer alguns estudos particulares... mas sim, estás muito bem, querido."

# game/Scenes/Update20/loveinterestmontage.rpy:283
translate portuguese loveinterestmontage_cc1fc6d9:

    # sst "... but I hate failing people, especially when I can tell that they're trying."
    sst "... mas detesto reprovar pessoas, especialmente quando vejo que estão a esforçar-se."

# game/Scenes/Update20/loveinterestmontage.rpy:284
translate portuguese loveinterestmontage_d70fddc8:

    # sst "So you're good. You'll pass."
    sst "Então estás bem. Vais passar."

# game/Scenes/Update20/loveinterestmontage.rpy:285
translate portuguese loveinterestmontage_3484a643:

    # pc "Thanks so much, Ms. Welch."
    pc "Muito obrigada, Sra. Welch."

